{"tid":813541,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"原來公屋師奶傾計話題都可以係新樓盤","createTime":"2018-09-10T13:43:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-13T12:09:51.000Z","uid":144063,"like":18,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"55eb5d90e2f1956d79518ff616d4439234c5221c","tid":813541,"uid":144063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T13:43:51.000Z","msg":"今日食飯時聽到兩個公屋師奶傾計<br />\n<br />\n師奶A : 我大陸黎既親戚最近啊 派左去安泰邨喎 好新好靚啊果到 間屋又大喎 400呎 6個人住<br />\n<br />\n師奶B : 車 山卡啦地方 都唔夠我住果到好(元洲邨) 樓下就地鐵站 去邊到都近 不知幾方便  又多野食<br />\n<br />\n師奶A : 咁又係既 不過遲下上水彩園都會起新公屋 派到果到都唔錯 上去(大陸)又方便<br />\n<br />\n師奶B : 柴灣果邊起緊既都唔錯啊 住港島區人又高級d 又冇咁多人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家公屋師奶傾計話題都可以係新樓盤"},{"pid":"81b98b33c832dfe92a953027a4fe4d9bb24c3674","tid":813541,"uid":144063,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T14:01:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"281fc519e9d8a7745b11a798b9e2640a0d251f5d","tid":813541,"uid":144063,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T14:07:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef2b1ea75f5cbce63448705a9d9d695a7e91180e","tid":813541,"uid":55851,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T14:09:19.000Z","msg":"3/10<br />\n下次作好啲，啲內容太單調"},{"pid":"c2c4964cabc0e9301a3ca8f2ccb112bf7b4dae4e","tid":813541,"uid":144063,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"ef2b1ea75f5cbce63448705a9d9d695a7e91180e","tid":813541,"uid":55851,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T14:09:19.000Z","msg":"3/10<br />\n下次作好啲，啲內容太單調"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T14:11:06.000Z","msg":"比你老母分<br />\n真人真事"},{"pid":"0ea0006484420023d3855384699f4ebfd2a0dbca","tid":813541,"uid":144063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T14:19:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},